# iOS / Swift Rules

- Use SwiftUI for the sample Settings screen.
- Platform-native controls (UISwitch, SF Symbols) are **hold** candidates — do not propagate native control swaps to Android.
- Brand tokens (colors, spacing scale, typography) are **propagate** candidates.
- Prefer design tokens over hardcoded hex values. Hardcoded values are **flag** candidates.
- Minimum touch target: 44pt.
- System font is SF Pro (hold). Brand font changes propagate.
